[[File:Dock.jpg|thumb|250px|A merchant space dock]]
A '''merchant space dock ''' was an [[Orbit/Legends|orbital]] gathering place for independent [[Starship/Legends|ship]] [[Captain/Legends|captains]] looking to pick up additional work. These small independent orbital [[Space station/Legends|stations]] provided a place for ship captains to gather and an opportunity for [[Fleet/Legends|fleet]] [[Commander/Legends|commanders]] to recruit them into their local defense forces for additional support.

